ener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="美伊协议刺激看涨情绪，企业纷纷借入现金"&gt;正试图规避风险&lt;/a&gt;。美国杠杆贷款基金已连续 10 周流入，从 2 月底开始的多周低迷中恢复过来，伊朗战争给已经因人工智能颠覆担忧而陷入困境的市场增添了不确定性。对于寻求出售新收购债务的银行和私募股权公司来说，需求上升是一个可喜的迹象。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure style="margin: 20px 0;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/olbdHAz9LVgRxyBywYHUN-H22bMSX703-wqxGl75R1vqCclPx6YwX8Urayg82H_OcXtBeZOntOBGSeIpFA2MQsTFZHTrb4reL6KQY0fZrxJyzWstY7AkH_ynhNKmx5VfDEmh_MgIf8OfewdLc45_vj79IaiZ-nrbEoQl4siPr_Qxv0XGlUOTxXkdREEVqt3JkCcca_yEXjjejSHzSlJ7-rr-HA3MS7bd1rXl4zL8UFIqe_F9xrRhCijPFqVQGWuQKyicQ7QFAc5CjOdyQ7AABw3xFixxkTpcQbxYfBKfUhmPwrn4AQP-x9VwJehD63qnF-Tk6I5AvQ-wUowpwg5xqLW4W7_4_O1U5eur_1SpXnxYJ7HMKlZeyB1jxMg1PRUlsfpHLEpo9iuBzqMlC4_2CraDOjd1z8cgUau0yE1bUY1XpWBFPqvQhXYcXubTiagYU6bVxP39PTY3yJZjyPz3-X1dWUrfHpd_Mcix63eM7qNY67LcYuZIQpn5Bz6_LZ7FaxPU85gwzHuzoDAvAqS6l_o66zA/l5-IqGScY6oCk-Q0Zy2LTW3UtRfw5H60/21" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="580"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iNxa3w66IEPI/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" alt="" width="580"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="替代" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iNxa3w66IEPI/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" style="width: 100%; display: block; margin-bottom: 4px;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/figure&gt;&lt;hr style="border-top: 1px solid; margin-top: 24px;" /&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt; &lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;SpaceX 股价自创纪录的首次公开募股以来首次下跌&lt;/strong&gt;， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/ORbJ4Iaehag_TtUxlGtmUPPl39K9kkmjjnzkVcb_7MUIuZTrMOVzlelwRrrIDQ061Y8CrEhXbjrjH1aYRbzzkcU1_ewgxCKXBBo5j54W_tmTGh4oQ78GclZAwTClkh5z31WMC4wbESr-JXrOC-hwDH2vubPFeItXHwwEpHSn6en5QxLbwgLTwATHEqn1qBYle