: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;澳大利亚极右翼反对党领袖宝琳·汉森（&lt;/strong&gt; Pauline Hanson）呼吁建立一个“ &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/ouyod3gBn9_IPED0ezJdrSBm72dt2u9kM8qLzvQetfW2T3352kE_sbfJrFq90nNa0_6nvwHYsCCtc5ECQb-R8vQDFETu_9avAGIwqeR_9Jk7p6uBiqUeNj0XbQdIH4q4OGfU73xRn8H9FAHom-X-obsJa-U7s_yuRQX3T-k0RpfBiO8C2-C_0lSQpXuxusR0f4ZGO1DgPVeATH9fnkiTeL-t9sZJsbfPf68HMb7M73H4mwxc5VxKo77XGyvG-hAkegOrk6RLRbVfBAJE_Z7UOher7tutW6A-9srIzhILDmnEc6CNgeJr-ej53e4UOAup1LOCxg8u8tQgP0OIEHrWJz4jsplOfgF7Rbta8c2duBVzf3pgkAOlmlC11v6cr6It2TN-hdJv0dgsUV5XqxyE5sejT24-rn7rk2TwvjeM0LHT74Hv7KtALs1HNho3IG5yPFrfnI10GrXuCafN2pcPzAyln-lVptBL7lDn4u-S-hbGF__4pr2BApRuU26TnIfQkCw0N6Y28uNjy0Adp743GYRvDPY8qF-SC-jScY1A/2Dk4J1ZGJonPR0qomvLFquDZc5pnMktj/21" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="One Nation 的汉森表示，澳大利亚必须是“单一文化”"&gt;单一文化社会&lt;/a&gt;”，拒绝该国几十年来的多元文化主义，并将其住房危机归咎于大量移民。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;巴西最高法院&lt;/strong&gt;裁定前议员爱德华多·博尔索纳罗犯有试图&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/dc3qfOBnelqwhYrnjqH31Sf1tRVDhNXo-k4eANeIT3BRzkKS_Xs4scZEfLe0mlxkgOBM4dGqbSdF9MKr2AuyW5SdfQCC1Kw_mPnGnpvDL7vdcJxVH818uNu0bhtpegcGPK0eAb07k9IB2tRkzXM5oj-_trGDqKnSdJrOOW6PeyKMz6yb35KkghxzgKohG8OHZIM5S31kCANwQyJ9iECT10I0tXnLsXPwQmaO3t8GgluWgVWfg-loL_huR0tLIre9RxSfqYsoelyxLinE7EPOc5n5cf_yULGUmOFL7VhirSeHR6Jaud0E7NWsehsh38HnD31NBXhdgSuVgqxGmvoFdCqPpS6ZGt6Vh3yE6FrZDP-hM5dBa6ofKxqfnD_hJsA3xMRn-kadp-CdODX-O3q3KGCNcgTjGHsP4GQigWtZhYJH4DH7hrObe38Ls4iUIygndtjUkv9T6BnpzQ_43ImMgeQsqbzGxlkDzeLmnhoiwkCHpRojqWUaw3uThSiIQdFTofSfr-NuiylQd3XBptKE8KClYSI5ujh_jYXFaXKivOX7yQ/NtWSqkiacdoNvfTOSeYBKN5I2wfGLvn2/21" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="巴西法院以干扰审判罪判处博尔索纳罗之子有罪"&gt;非法干扰&lt;/a&gt;与其父亲、前总统雅伊尔·博尔索纳罗审判相关的司法程序的罪名。博尔索纳罗因在 2022 年大选失败后策划政变而被定罪。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"